      <title>巴基斯坦通胀放缓，因需求疲软抵消能源成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/pakistan-inflation-slows-as-weak-demand-offsets-energy-cost-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费需求放缓的影响抵消了能源价格上涨的影响，巴基斯坦 7 月份通胀率放缓至两年半多以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/pakistan-inflation-slows-as-weak-demand-offsets-energy-cost-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 09:36:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新单位助力阿达尼旗舰业务利润增长 115%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/adani-flagship-s-profit-surges-115-on-airports-mining-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿达尼企业有限公司 (Adani Enterprises Ltd.) 公布季度利润增长 115%，得益于一些新业务的推动，亿万富翁高塔姆阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 的旗舰业务从去年严厉的卖空者攻击中反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/adani-flagship-s-profit-surges-115-on-airports-mining-revenue</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 09:30:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
